collection.name: DinoBabies - Ziggy's Landing
collection.description:
Staked Ziggys as of 5/8/22 : 2340

Dino Babies in Space is more than an NFT project, it is a community first animated series created by Matt Bolinger. Each of the 5,500 Genesis Dino Babies allows its holder to participate in the Dino Babies in Space community treasury and vote on every aspect of the show’s production. By owning a Ziggy, you’re taking part in the full creation process of the next animated action-comedy.

Check out all the parts of the project below: Honey Brasco Space Pirates
https://opensea.io/collection/honeybrascospacepirates
